verses.text: Mamin Jehová, ol walnhej t'a in b'it to toxonton ay a wach'k'olal. D'a masanil tiempo ol waleli to yel tzak'elk'och tas tzala'.
Ha yab'ixal a wach'k'olal ay t'a masanil tiempo ol waleli. Ol walanpaxeli to max k'exmaj tas tzala', icha yaj juntzanh tas ay t'a satcha’anh.
Alnac: Ay jun in trato yet' winhaj Dawid in chekab' ix in sik'eli, ix wak'kan in ti' t'a winh, ix walan t'a winh icha tik:
Ha heb' inhtilal, ol wak'nhejkanoch heb' reyal a k'exuloc t'a masanil tiempo, xin chi.
Mamin Jehová, masanil heb' molanek' t'a satcha’anh, ol sb'itej heb' tas satub'tac tza k'ulej. Ol yalpaxel heb' to tzak'elk'och tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, malaj junocxo mach t'a satcha’anh syal slajb'an sb'a ed'oc. Malaj junok heb' lajan ed'oc.
Te niwan elk'och t'a skal heb' ángel. Te ay a poder t'a yichanh heb' oyanoch t'a a patic ichanh.
Mamin Jehová Yajal t'a Smasanil, ¿mach wal junocxo lajan ed'oc? Masanil tas syalnhej uuj. Tzak'elk'och masanil tas tzala'.
Yol a k'ab' ayek' ha' mar ayic ste owaj ha'. Ha achxo tzak'och waan ha' ayic ste k'anh ha'.
Ha nok' nok' ay smay t'a yol ha' mar, ix ach k'e tek'tek' t'a yib'anh nok', ix a tek'ancham nok'. Ix a saclemej heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayach yuj a poder.
Ha satcha’anh yet' sat lum tik, ic toni. Ha ach a b'onac yol yib'anhk’inal tik yet' masanil tastac ay t'ay.
Ha norte masanto sk'och t'a sur, a ach ix a b'o'o. Ha lum witzal Tabor yet' lum witzal Hermón, sb'itan lum t'ayach.
Ha a k'ab' te ay yip. Ha a wach' k'ab', masanil syal yuj.
Ha a despacho te tek'an yaj yuj a wach'il yet' a tojolal. Ha t'a masanil scheclajel a wach'k'olal, tzak'an elk'och tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, te wach' yic heb' anima tzach b'itani. Tzalajk'olalnhej yic heb' yuj a wach'k'olal.
Ha wal t'ayach syak' tzalajb'oc sk'ol heb'. Yuj a tojolal tz'ik'jichaanh heb'.
D'a wal yel, te niwan ipalil tzak' t'ayonh. Yuj a wach'k'olal syalnhej cuuj.
Mamin Jehová, ko Kolumal aji. Ach ko Diosal a onh israel onh tik, ko Reyal ach.

Ha t'a peka', ix ach lolon t'a wayichal, ix alan t'a heb' a chekab' tzach k'anab'ajan icha tik: Ix in och yet' jun soldado te tek'an, aton jun mach sik'b'ilel wuj t'a skal in chonhab', ix wak'an yopisio.
Ix ilchaj winhaj Dawid in chekab' wuuj, a yet' waceite yic sik'wal ix in ch'oxo' to reyxo yaj winh.
Manh ol in och waan in kolwaj t'a winh, yujto a in poder ol ak'an yip winh.
Ha heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a winh, manh ol yal-laj yoch sk'ab' heb' t'a winh. Ha heb' sk'ulan chukal, manh ol tzak'wanlaj heb' t'a winh.
Ol in tek'kanem heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a winh. Ol in milancham heb' schichonoch sk'ol t'a winh.
Ayinnhej ek' yet' winh yujto xajan winh wuuj. Ol wak' elk'och tas swala'. Vuujnhej ol yalnhej yuj winh.
Ol wak' niwanb'oc smacb'en winh. Ol schael yich t'ha ha' mar Mediterráneo masanto sk'och t'ha ha' niwan Éufrates.
Ol yalan winh t'ayin: In Mam ach, in Diosal ach, a t'ayach tzin col in b'a, xcham winh.
Ha inxo ol wak' sniwanil yelk'och winh, icha junok b'ab'el unin. Yelxo wal ek'alto sniwanil ol aj yelk'och winh t'a yichanh masanil heb' rey.
Ol in xajanej winh t'a junelnhej. Ha in trato yet' winh, manh ol k'exmajlaj.
Ha heb' yinhtilal winh ol ak'an reyal sk'exuloc, ol b'eynhejb'atoc yacb'an ayto ek' satcha’anh tik.
Palta tato ol yaktejkan in k'ayb'ub'al heb' yinhtilal winh chi', tato manh ol sk'anab'ajej heb' tas swala',
tato manh ol sb'eyb'alej in b'eyb'al heb', tato manh ol sk'anab'ajej in lolonel heb' swak' sk'ulej,
ol wak'och syaelal heb' yet' te' jixk'ab'te' yuj spital. Ol in mak' heb' yet' nok' tz'um yuj schukal.
Axo pax winhaj Dawid jun, manh ol wactejkan in xajanan winh, ol wak'nhejelk'och in ti' ix wak' t'a winh.
Manh ol ek'b'atlaj in trato yet' winh. Ol wak'nhejelk'och tas ix walkan t'a winh.
D'a junelnhej ix wak'kan in ti' t'a winhaj Dawid chi', a in ix wak' testigoal in b'a to manh ol in k'exa'.
Ha heb' yinhtilal winh ol ak'an reyal sk'exuloc t'a wichanh t'a masanil tiempo icha yaj yoc k'u tik.
Tek'annhej ol ajek' heb' yak'an yajalil, icha yaj k'een uj t'a satcha’anh, xa chi.
Axo ticnaik Mamin, ix a chakkanel winh rey a sik'nakkanelta, ix a patiquejkanel winh. Ix cot owal t'a winh.
Maj ak'elk'och a trato t'a winh a chekab' chi'. Ix a yumcanel scorona winh t'a sat lu'um.
Man jantacoc ix aj yolanil masanil smuroal schonhab' winh. Ix ak' juwoquem schonhab' winh.
Ha heb' anima tzek' ta', masanil tas ay t'a chonhab' chi', syelk'ejb'at heb'. Ha heb' ay t'a slak'anil winh, sb'uchwaj heb' t'a winh.
Ha ach ix ak' sk'ulej heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a winh, syik'anchaanh sk'ab' heb' yuj tzalajk'olal.
Ix ik'el ye k'een yespada winh. Maj ach ochlaj yet' winh ayic ix och owal.
Ix ak' lajwoc sb'inajnaquil winh. Ix a yumankanem sdespacho winh t'a sat lu'um.
Ix pet ichamax winh uuj, niwan ix aj ak'an q'uixwelal winh.
Mamin Jehová, ¿b'aq'uinh ol actej a k'ub'anel a b'a? ¿Ichanhej am tik ol ajcot yowal a k'ol icha junok owal k'ak'?
Mamin, nacoti to a ko k 'inal tzapan toni. Ha onh anima onh tik, tzapan ix utejkan ko k 'inal.
Malaj junok anima to malaj b'ak'uinh ol chamoc. Malaj mach syal scolan sb'ha t'a yol sk'ab' chamel.
Mamin, ¿b'ajtil ay a wach'k'olal a ch'oxnac t'a peka', aton ak'annac a ti' t'a winhaj Dawid, to ol ak' elk'och tas ix ala'?
Mamin, nacoti to manh jantacoc onh stzuntzan heb' anima a onh a chekab' onh tik. Pitz'anoch tas tzonh yutej heb' chi' t'a in pixan.
Mamin Jehová, a heb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayach tik, t'a junjun rato sb'uchwaj heb' t'a winh a chekab' sik'b'ilel uuj.
Alchajokab' wach' lolonel t'a Jehová t'a masanil tiempo. Ujokab'i.
